							<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://carlchenet.com/2013/12/31/virtual-environments-with-python-3-3/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2013-12-31T00:00:53+00:00">décembre 31, 2013</time><time class="updated" datetime="2013-12-31T01:15:44+00:00">décembre 31, 2013</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://carlchenet.com/author/carlchenet/">Carl Chenet</a></span></span>
				
