			<footer class="entry-meta">
							<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://carlchenet.com/2013/12/26/cadeau-de-noel-publication-de-brebis-0-9-le-verificateur-automatise-de-sauvegarde/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2013-12-26T00:01:15+00:00">décembre 26, 2013</time><time class="updated" datetime="2013-12-26T00:01:46+00:00">décembre 26, 2013</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://carlchenet.com/author/carlchenet/">Carl Chenet</a></span></span>
				
