			<footer class="entry-meta">
							<span class="posted-on"><a href="http://carlchenet.com/2013/11/09/brebis-0-8-the-fully-automated-backup-checker-released/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2013-11-09T13:54:38+00:00">novembre 9, 2013</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://carlchenet.com/author/carlchenet/">Carl Chenet</a></span></span>
				
							
